==English==
===Nominal phrase===
'''triple play'''

#{{baseball}} A [[defensive]] [[play]] in which three [[out]]s are recorded
#: ''There has only ever been one un-assisted '''triple play''' recorded in the World Series.''
# A [[service]] offering where three services are offered together, notably voice, data, and video service
#: ''The local cable company is offering a '''triple play''' service.''